## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="8a0b9-102">当用户通过调用 `new` 或 <xref:System.Activator.CreateInstance%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 并在线程返回到用户代码之前，创建新的客户端激活对象的实例时，<xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Activation.IConstructionCallMessage> 将发送到远程应用程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a0b9-102">When the user creates an instance of a new client-activated object by calling `new` or <xref:System.Activator.CreateInstance%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> and before the thread returns to the user code, a <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Activation.IConstructionCallMessage> is sent to the remote application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a0b9-103">当构造消息到达远程应用程序时，它由远程处理程序激活器（默认值）或在 <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Activation.IConstructionCallMessage.Activator%2A> 属性中指定的消息进行处理，并且将创建一个新的对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a0b9-103">When the construction message arrives at the remote application, it is processed by a remoting activator (either the default one, or one that is specified in the <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Activation.IConstructionCallMessage.Activator%2A> property) and a new object is created.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a0b9-104">远程处理应用程序随后会将 <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Activation.IConstructionReturnMessage> 返回到本地应用程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a0b9-104">The remoting application then returns a <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Activation.IConstructionReturnMessage> to the local application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a0b9-105"><xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Activation.IConstructionReturnMessage> 包含 <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.ObjRef>的实例，该实例对有关远程对象的信息进行打包。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a0b9-105">The <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Activation.IConstructionReturnMessage> contains an instance of <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.ObjRef>, which packages information about the remote object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a0b9-106">远程处理基础结构将 <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.ObjRef> 实例转换为向用户代码返回的远程对象的代理。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a0b9-106">The remoting infrastructure converts the <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.ObjRef> instance into a proxy to the remote object, which is returned to the user code.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
